  abilityName: Pack Tactics
  description: 'Use before attacking with at least one ally.

    You may combine
    any number of dice into

    larger dice with a value equal to the total of

    the
    combined dice, to a maximum of d12

    Damage. For example, combining a d4 and
    a

    d8 into a d12.'
